text: Jean Guillou (24 June 1931 - 29 August 2019) was a French gymnast. He competed at the 1952 Summer Olympics and the 1956 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1931 births Category:2019 deaths Category:French male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1956 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
